{"tid":2191566,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"受累疫情！調查指南韓逾七成公司沒有招聘計劃","createTime":"2020-09-06T13:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T13:56:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa14aa946e7d0e6402288901f82b9ccc20deb51c","tid":2191566,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wSz0BtO5v0r30BeBrHhf9A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/3be38e0713e363ced86730921bed9adb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwSz0BtO5v0r30BeBrHhf9A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F3be38e0713e363ced86730921bed9adb&h=63be774c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4mCkd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=07881cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】新冠肺炎疫情對就業市場造成嚴重衝擊，外媒引述南韓經濟研究所調查顯示，今年下半年當地3/4大公司沒有招聘計劃。調查針對南韓銷售額前500大公司進行，得到120家公司回覆。<br />\n<br />\n南韓就業市場下半年情況恐比上半年更嚴峻。調查顯示，半數公司表示還沒有制定招聘計劃，另有24.2%表示不會在下半年提供工作機會。在今年下半年有招聘計劃的公司中，僅22.6%公司表示將比去年招聘更多員工。被問調整招聘計劃計劃的原因，近70%公司指乃受到疫情所影響。<br />\n<br />\n另因應疫情，有超過19%公司透露已經採用遠端招聘系統，35%公司則正在考慮使用這種網路招聘系統。"},{"pid":"190c9c581b653f170db0273f8ed399c2a4fa8983","tid":2191566,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"冇人走咪唔駛請人"}]}